(7467, 'Rosucholest 20mg 20 tabs', 'روزوكوليست 20مجم 20 قرص', '', '94', 'Rosuvastatin', 'Averos pharma', 'Tab', 'أقراص', '', '', '20mg', 'The FDA monograph states that rosuvastatin is indicated as an adjunct to diet in the treatment of triglyceridemia, Primary Dysbetalipoproteinemia (Type III Hyperlipoproteinemia), and Homozygous Familial Hypercholesterolemia.[F4649]
